Table.tsx", "source_location": "L437"}, {"caller_nid": "components_nodestable_nodestable", "callee": "filter", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "/Users/omkard/Documents/goworkspace/src/github.com/platform9/vjailbreak/ui/src/features/agents/components/NodesTable.tsx", "source_location": "L437"}]}